platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: We’d be lost without Dropbox—it’s an indispensable part of our digital toolbox. But for all its usefulness, the thing we appreciate most about this cloud-storage app is how little we have to think about it. Whether we’re sharing documents between devices, uploading photos directly from our camera, or emailing large files to friends, it all just works—seamlessly and effortlessly.
這款雲端儲存 App 非常實用，最令我們欣賞的一點是它的用法非常簡單直接。無論我們共享或上載任何檔案，一切都能輕鬆流暢地順利進行。

For all its usefulness, the thing we appreciate most about this cloud-storage app is how little we have to think about it. Whatever we’re sharing or uploading, it all just works – seamlessly and effortlessly.
驚くほど便利なだけでなく、使い方に悩むこともほぼ無く使うことができるクラウドストレージアプリです。ファイルの共有もアップロードも、とにかく楽々とスムーズにこなせます。

For all its usefulness, the thing we appreciate most about this cloud-storage app is how little we have to think about it. Whatever we’re sharing or uploading, it all just works–seamlessly and effortlessly.
這款 App 就像你的雲端儲存管家，不只功能實用，使用體驗也十分流暢。無論是分享或上傳檔案，它都能輕鬆達成任務，完全不用你操心。
Au-delà de sa grande utilité, ce qu’on apprécie le plus dans cette app de stockage cloud, c’est le peu de prise de tête. Quoi qu’on partage ou importe, tout fonctionne avec fluidité et simplicité.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: All your files safe in one place across all your devices.
All your files are safe in one place across all your devices.
Tous vos fichiers au même endroit et sur tous vos appareils.
